1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:05,147
-Oh, my God.
And so by the finale,
-I was completely dehydrated.
-You're welcome.

2
00:00:05,147 --> 00:00:08,048
-And by the way,
the Russian accent was awesome.

3
00:00:08,048 --> 00:00:10,642
-Thanks. Yeah. Um, I actually
do all kinds of accents.

4
00:00:10,642 --> 00:00:12,310
-Really?
-Yeah.

5
00:00:12,310 --> 00:00:15,700
Did someone
say all kinds of accents?

6
00:00:15,700 --> 00:00:19,775
Well, I reckon this here show
ain't big enough
for the both of us.

7
00:00:19,775 --> 00:00:24,399
-[ Southern accent ]
I reckon it ain't, partner.

8
00:00:24,693 --> 00:00:26,934
-It's an accent duel.

9
00:00:26,934 --> 00:00:29,071
Come on,
let's get out of the way.

10
00:00:29,071 --> 00:00:30,609
-Y'all ready?

11
00:00:30,609 --> 00:00:32,891
-Call 'em out.
-German!

12
00:00:32,891 --> 00:00:36,396
-Oh, das ist easier than
drinking ein Hefeweizen, ja?

13
00:00:36,396 --> 00:00:37,610
-Cajun!

14
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,539
-[ Cajun accent ] I was taking my fambo down there
Lake Pon-char-chon Way.

15
00:00:40,539 --> 00:00:43,843
-French.
-[ French accent ] But what do
you mean, everyone wears Croc
to the airport?

16
00:00:43,843 --> 00:00:46,108
-Shakespeare!
-To be or not to be?

17
00:00:46,108 --> 00:00:47,331
-That is the question.

18
00:00:47,331 --> 00:00:49,372
-Now Shakespeare but bad.

19
00:00:49,372 --> 00:00:51,653
-[ British accent ] To be or
not to be. That's the question.

20
00:00:51,653 --> 00:00:53,312
What's up with this guy,
am I right?

21
00:00:53,312 --> 00:00:54,058
-Jamaican.

22
00:00:54,058 --> 00:00:57,533
-I feel like guys like us -should probably not --
-Yeah, that's not --
I don't think
that's a good idea.

23
00:00:57,533 --> 00:01:00,428
-Okay. Sorry. What about
a Na'vi from "Avatar"?

24
00:01:00,428 --> 00:01:02,575
-[ Jamaican accent ] I seeing ya
clear as Mother Eywa, mon.

25
00:01:02,575 --> 00:01:05,446
-Shrek!
-Get out my swamp, Donkey.

26
00:01:05,446 --> 00:01:07,512
-Italian!
-[ As Mario ] Here we go!

27
00:01:07,512 --> 00:01:10,250
-Russian!
-[ Russian accent ]
When you get to hell,

28
00:01:10,250 --> 00:01:12,919
tell them Rosanov sent you.

29
00:01:14,506 --> 00:01:15,691
You got me.

30
00:01:15,691 --> 00:01:17,080
-Yay!
-Yay!

31
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:19,459
-I won. I won.
-Good job, man. That was great.

32
00:01:19,459 --> 00:01:21,191
-Is he okay?

33
00:01:21,191 --> 00:01:22,634
-James!
-James.

34
00:01:22,634 --> 00:01:25,115
-Ja-- He's not breathing!
-You okay?

35
00:01:25,115 --> 00:01:27,753
-You killed him!
-Uh, medic?!

36
00:01:27,753 --> 00:01:29,945
Can we get a medic?!

37
00:01:30,429 --> 00:01:33,761
-Stop. Relax. Stop!

